text: Hakim Sadi (born 14 November 1992) is an Algerian long distance runner. He placed 104th in the marathon at the 2016 Summer Olympics. ==References== ==External links== * Category:1992 births Category:Living people Category:Algerian male long-distance runners Category:Algerian male marathon runners Category:Place of birth missing (living people) Category:Athletes (track and field) at the 2016 Summer Olympics Category:Olympic athletes of Algeria
